text: Claire Smith (born 10 April 1963) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa
